																	<p>As a member of the U.S. Senate Budget Committee, I am more than aware that a $17 trillion dollar national debt and a $700 billion deficit are serious problems that must be addressed.</p> <p>But I am also aware that real unemployment is close to 14 percent, that tens of millions...</p>								
							</div>				

							<div class="read_post">
								<a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/rep-bernie-sanders/for-a-budget-that-is-both_b_4170193.html">Read Post</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
